column3: Temporarily closing to upgrade to db4.8, wx2.9.2 and miniupnpc1.6 on win32\n
OK, think this one is finally good to go.\n
Closing again until I have a minute to get devrandom's upgrades which make mingw results deterministic pulled into this.\n(very much want this stuff for 0.4).\n
OK, Im doing a couple final run-throughs and then I'd like to see this as the build system for 0.4\n

It would be nice to get a confirmation that the results here are deterministic...IIRC devrandom said that there are a few bytes changing in the final nsis exe, but everything else should be stable (including the boost and wx results).  Im going to see if I can work on the nsis exe, but Ill leave this open because if it doesnt happen before 0.4 is ready to go, its fine by me.\n
